{
  "id": "63a701ed99eec8001d39f324",
  "title": "権利と正しさ",
  "created": 1671889390,
  "updated": 1671889390,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63a701ed99eec8001d39f324",
      "text": "権利と正しさ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fcd",
      "text": "from [権利とは]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fce",
      "text": "権利と正しさ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fcf",
      "text": ">That which complies with justice, law or reason. ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fd0",
      "text": " > We're on the side of right in this contest.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fd1",
      "text": "> A legal, just or moral entitlement.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fd2",
      "text": " > You have no right to go through my personal diary.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fd3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fd4",
      "text": "そもそも英語で[right]って言葉に「[正義]・[正しさ]」という意味と「権利」という意味が重なってるあたり、概念を適切に分割できてなさそうなきな臭さがある[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fd5",
      "text": "　正義に適ってるものが「正しさ」で、法に適ってるものが「権利」という考え方なのかなぁ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fd6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fd7",
      "text": "　>日本語の「権利」という言葉には、「正しい」という意味は含まれていない。逆に、「権」という言葉は「力」(power)という意味を含んでいるから、「権利」は、自分の利益を力ずくでおし通すといったニュアンスをもつ。だから、「権利ばかりを主張するのは問題だ」といわれたりする。しかし、この命題の「権利」を“right”におきかえてみれば、それが成り立ちえない命題であることがすぐにわかる。「right(正しいこと)ばかりを主張する」のに何の問題もないはずだからである。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fd8",
      "text": "　 https://www.pref.tottori.lg.jp/secure/316971/1point-2.pdf",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fd9",
      "text": "　 この切り口は面白い[nishio.icon][amemiya.icon]",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
      "id": "63a701edaff09e00007e6fda",
      "text": "　　権利の権の字は権力、実権、権威、権益、特権、権限…などに使われる字",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889390,
      "updated": 1671889390
    },
    {
